cu.explanation_en: Setting the remote SCTP port to 0 will cause connection failure to the DU as port 0 is invalid and unreachable, leading to F1 interface setup rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the remote network port to 0 will cause connection failure to the CU as port 0 is invalid and unreachable, leading to F1 interface setup rejection.
du.explanation_zh: 將遠端網路端口設定為 0 會導致與 CU 的連接失敗，因為端口 0 無效且不可達，導致 F1 介面設定被拒絕。
